## final solution
```xml
		&lt;dependency&gt;
			&lt;groupId&gt;io.quarkiverse.githubapp&lt;/groupId&gt;
			&lt;artifactId&gt;quarkus-github-app&lt;/artifactId&gt;
			&lt;version&gt;1.16.0&lt;/version&gt;
		&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

