[![enter image description here][2]][2]

i.e. 3 rows have been inserted using each of the fixes.


  [1]: https://developer.android.com/reference/android/database/sqlite/SQLiteDatabase#insert(java.lang.String,%20java.lang.String,%20android.content.ContentValues)
